lead_paragraph: When the epic, drama-drenched Game 7 was briefly delayed by rain, Indians players returned to their clubhouse, where chairs had been removed and plastic sheets hung in anticipation for a party waiting to pop since 1948.

headline.print_headline: End Game: Indians Can't Finish Off Amazing Season With Title
